      "role": "user",
      "content": "i havent been able to sleep much lately... everything feels so different. i was walking near the old grove today and the way the birds were behaving, it was like they were signaling something specific to me. it felt like a confirmation of what i've been feeling deep down, like i have a specific purpose that i'm finally waking up to. do you think it's possible for the natural world to communicate that kind of direction to someone?",
